name.text: Zero Fucks Presents: ZERO FUTURE
name.html: Zero Fucks Presents: ZERO FUTURE

description.text:
The Zero Fucks crew is stoked to bring you ZERO FUTURE - a night of cutting-edge future bass, grime, garage and breaks!  
What is ZERO FUTURE?  
As dance music genres continue to hit escape velocity, they often go careening out of control and occasionally slam straight into one another. For many, this is what is exciting about music - the amount of new songs that combine subgenres or push the envelope forward. ZERO FUTURE is a celebration of that next level, and the era of unique new music coming out every week on the internet.

name.text: House of Bass: Outside Lands Afterparty: All Fun Music Edition
name.html: House of Bass: Outside Lands Afterparty: All Fun Music Edition

description.text:
Presale is closed! $10 at the door all night long! 
ZERO FUCKS brings back HOUSE OF BASS to the Public Works loft on Friday, August 7! You're going to need to dance after Outside Lands - actually, instead of going to Outside Lands, take the day off work, go to the spa, and get good and rested to dance your ass off on the dance floor widely renowned as SF's friendliest. We've got Zero Fucks regular DJ SPACECAMP, who majored in Fun at (where else) Space Camp, and up from LA we've got CHEWY CHIPS - her hair is fun, but only half as fun as her record collection, and last but not least RATIONALE who.. well.. let's just say he knows something about something that starts with F. 
DEEP HOUSE - TECH HOUSE - BASS HOUSE - BOOTY SHAKING BREAKSY HOUSE - HOUSEY HOUSE - FUN HOUSE 
By now you know the drill: drink specials, free with RSVP, hundreds of your new best friends, hugs from the DJs, and smiling until your face falls off. Be there or regret it.

name.text: Zero Fucks: House of Bass - 1 Year Anniversary
name.html: Zero Fucks: House of Bass - 1 Year Anniversary

description.text:
Time flies when you're dancing to HOUSE. MUSIC. 
How has it been a full year already!??!  Shoutout to everyone who's come and danced it out in the Public Works Loft with us for an entire orbit around the sun <3  
This month, come celebrate the Zero Fucks 1-year and the fact that we're all a little older, a little wiser, a little sexier, and a little more rad.  Decompress or just shake off the week to the freshest Deep House / Tech House beats from your friendly neighborhood DJs.

description.text:

First up, during the primetime slot is Unk'l Funk'l - you might recognize him from Duckpond, or any of his numerous awesome sets around the Bay, including last month on a party bus that we flew into space. Wait, you missed that? Get a sense of his vibes with this mix he recorded at a NIMBY party: 
 
Opening up the night will be a new face to the Zero Fucks crowd, Oakland's ArchieXX, who helped build the OLOW afterhours in the East Bay. Check out a recent set from him here:  
 
We'll of course have support from the magical Zero Fucks DJs + VJs, and we'll be in our favorite spot, the Oddjob Loft at Public Works. Are you ready? RSVP for free already so that you don't miss out!
